conditions to be met, for making a lander, steal a human

DRAFT 1.0
---------
1.Are there any humans to steal (YES > step2, NO > step 10)
2.Is there a stealer already spawned (YES > step10, NO step 3)
3.Are there are any landers to turn into a stealer (YES > step4, NO > step10)
4.Choose 1 lander from the landers, that are on screen
  (probability of changing into a stealer 1\1000)

10. Do nothing

DRAFT 2.0
---------
1.Are there any humans to steal (YES > step2, NO > step 10)
2.Is there a stealer already spawned (YES > step10, NO step 3)
3.Are there are any landers to turn into a stealer (YES > step4, NO > step10)
4.Is lander within distance to pickup a human (Check all humans) (YES > step5, NO > step10)
5.Probability to steal 1/500  (YES > step 6, NO > step 10)
6.turn lander into stealer

10. Do nothing

Conditions, for an existing stealers
------------------------------------
1.if human captured by player (turn stealer back into lander)
2.other wise, capture human

Gameplay for baiter
-------------------
After <ENTER TIME> a baiter will spawn in, if the level hasn't been cleared.
After every <ENTER TIME> another baiter will spawn in, and so on.....


ID numbers
-----------
0 = lander
1 = mutant
2 = bomber
3 = pod
4 = swarmer
5 = stealer
9 = humans
10 = moving bullet
11 = static bullet
12 = baiter

100 = anything in enemy array is dead, so delete it
